com.motorola.iden.call
Interface CallListener

public interface CallListener

A CallListener is an interface that listens to all registered types of calls. The CallListener is an interface that provides method to listen to any of InterConnectCall, Group Call, or Private Call. callActionListener method returns the type of call only if it is registered, and the state in which it is in.

Method Summary

          The method returns the type of a call and the state it is in.
